      <title>摩根大通关注瑞士企业业务增长和区块链推动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-eyes-swiss-corporate-business-gains-blockchain-boost-2024-09-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通的一位高管表示，摩根大通希望扩大其瑞士企业银行业务，并希望利用区块链服务来帮助获得客户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-eyes-swiss-corporate-business-gains-blockchain-boost-2024-09-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 13:31:28 GMT</pubDate>
