      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-issue-broad-measures-improve-insurance-sector-prevent-risks-2024-09-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一份声明称，中国国务院周三表示，将出台具体指导方针，加强保险业监管，防范保险业风险。]]></description>
